name: Ledger x Deadfellaz - Proof of Redemption

metadata.name: Ledgerfellaz
metadata.description: Created by the one-and-only Psych of Deadfellaz, the Ledgerfellaz token is issued each time a Deadfellaz Nano X Redemption Token is redeemed for the physical product. Like the redemption token, ownership of this token grants access to the Deadfellaz Discord server.
